## 3. Positioning Rules (AI Knowledge Pattern)

- **FAQ Position:** Always above the final CTA.
- **Testimonial Position:** Adjacent to FAQ (above or below) to maximize trust before conversion.
- **Background Rule:** No two identical background tiers should touch (Always alternate: White -> Shallow -> White -> Muted).

